            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新華保險首季歸母淨利按年升10.5% 新業務價值增長24.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新華保險(01336)公布，今年首季歸屬母公司股東淨利潤65.01億元(人民幣．下同)，較去年同期的58.82億元增長10.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：新華保險官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230725_FI_source-web_01336.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：新華保險官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230725_FI_source-web_01336.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：新華保險官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">扣除非經常性損益的歸母淨利潤達65.23億元，增長10.1%。營業數入221.33億元，則按年跌33.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">實現原保險保費收834.96億元，按年升14%；其中長期險首年期交保費244.51億元，增長25.6%，10年期及以上期交保費11.5億元，升1.13倍；續期保費收入532.93億元，增長20.7% ，持續發揮「壓艙石」作用。實現新業務價值46.55億元，增長24.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15939175-%e6%96%b0%e8%8f%af%e4%bf%9d%e9%9a%aa%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e6%ad%b8%e6%af%8d%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8710-5-%e6%96%b0%e6%a5%ad%e5%8b%99%e5%83%b9%e5%80%bc%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b724-7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/01336.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 17:46:58",
            "source": "bastillepost",
